GET THE JOB DONE

About
A little about your new handyman.


Your to-do list keeps growing? If you are in Ottawa or surrounding area and looking for a handyman, please call AP handy.work, where you will get professional, safe and reliable handyman work done on time. 

We are committed to providing you with dependable and skilled handy work, great customer service and first-class workmanship. 

AP handy.work completes all major or minor home repairs in a quick and efficient manner, thus making your to-do list manageable, which allows you to focus your energies on what you enjoy most. 

We strive to provide high quality service and ensure customer satisfaction. Simply put, we will do everything we can to meet or surpass your expectations.
